fi.tamk.cgeng.tiles

Class TileSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • fi.tamk.cgeng.tiles.TileSet

  • public class TileSet
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains set of Tiles, aswell as information about. every tile in the set. TileMap uses TileSet to draw these tiles to different positions.
